title: Stereo Microscope
description: A stereo microscope with a white body and dual eyepieces. It features a large base with a circular platform for placing specimens, and two adjustable focus knobs on the sides. The microscope is designed for three-dimensional viewing of small objects.

title: Microscope
description: A side view of a laboratory microscope, featuring a base, an arm, and an eyepiece. The microscope has multiple objective lenses and a stage for placing slides.

title: Test Tubes in a Rack
description: A laboratory rack holding five empty glass test tubes. The test tubes are arranged vertically and are clear, allowing visibility of their interior. The rack is made of a metallic material, providing support for the test tubes.

title: Pipette
description: A clear glass pipette with a yellow rubber bulb at the top. The pipette has measurement markings along its length, indicating volume levels.

title: Safety Gear
description: A pair of blue disposable gloves laid out flat, with a clear pair of safety goggles resting on top of them. The goggles have a green frame and a black strap.

title: Young Scientist at Work
description: An animated character, a young girl with long red hair tied back, is wearing safety goggles and gloves while working in a laboratory. She is seated at a table with a microscope in front of her and is using a pipette to transfer a liquid from a test tube. Next to her, there is a rack holding several colorful test tubes filled with different liquids.

title: Petri Dishes
description: A pair of clear glass petri dishes, one slightly elevated above the other. The dishes have a smooth surface and a greenish rim.
